{"tid":2114250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"合肥柏堰湖大壩放水,大量市民在下游河道撈魚","createTime":"2020-07-18T16:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T18:52:14.000Z","uid":36901,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"77425d0c99cf1a82744ebbd52f8ffbf71c4ce0a9","tid":2114250,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ahwang.cn/newsflash/20200718/2121450.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ahwang.cn%2Fnewsflash%2F20200718%2F2121450.html&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=b1d294ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ahwang.cn/newsflash/20200718/2121450.html</a><br />\n<br />\n安徽網大皖客戶端訊7月18日，合肥暴雨，有市民在網上爆料，位於合肥高新區的柏堰湖大壩洩水，大量魚兒跳出水面，吸引大量市民注意。18日下午4點 半，記者在合肥高新區柏堰湖大壩看到，還有市民不斷湧入柏堰湖濕地公園，很多人帶著網兜，桶等捕魚工具。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 記者在現場看到，柏堰湖大壩上和大壩下游河道兩邊，有大量市民在圍觀。在河道之中，數十名市民排成一排，用網在撈魚。<br />\n<br />\ncls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e150f95e47276933b844a966743a0a38465d952c","tid":2114250,"uid":139450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:21:16.000Z","msg":"點解帶兜捉魚都唔帶飲筒飲水"},{"pid":"30d0bb5532e8fb6be9940c3b273f498fb5d30422","tid":2114250,"uid":58209,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/BLzRYO6cn47irviPsxnxhoEXpUGBpJwxcyTO7EB8a42LDfC7_u7TbHQJRGPQC5QGQkGSfEaiCANcupFARM2h9U7Srsbt_4UQFtwLZ6mtaO4x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FBLzRYO6cn47irviPsxnxhoEXpUGBpJwxcyTO7EB8a42LDfC7_u7TbHQJRGPQC5QGQkGSfEaiCANcupFARM2h9U7Srsbt_4UQFtwLZ6mtaO4x&h=2a167db2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a15d7ece24a0aadd7a801c4183b40836a77d636","tid":2114250,"uid":305638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e150f95